Package: com.barabadev.sentinelcrash
Name: SentinelCrash
Version: 1.1.0
Architecture: iphoneos-arm64
Depends: firmware (>= 15.0)
Description: The most advanced rootless CrashReporter for iOS 15-18.
 Real-time crash monitoring across 19 system paths with automatic jailbreak detection.
 .
 Dopamine, palera1n, NathanLR, Procursus - iOS version range validation.
 Full signal and exception coverage including watchdog, jetsam, kernel panics, tweak/dylib crashes.
 .
 Dashboard - live monitoring, JB environment, crash stats.
 Crash Detail - stack trace (classic, IPS JSON, microstackshot) + raw log.
 Auto-Blame - identifies crash culprit via stack analysis and install correlation.
 Tweak Conflict Detector - ranks tweaks by danger score.
 Crash Grouping, Crash Diff, Timeline, Live Console.
 Export (JSON/text/Markdown), Symbolication, Analytics.
 iCloud Sync, 35 languages.
